Topics
======

Review of basic algebra skills including: factoring and graphing quadratic polynomials, solving quadratic equations, simplifying rational expresssions, solving rational equations, simplifying radical expressions, and solving radical equations. Successful completion or exemption of the MAT 094/MAT 095 sequence fully prepares the student for college level math.

